main event: On October 18, 1952, a number of people in Des Plaines, Illinois, reported a ground sighting of an unidentified flying object.
interesting points: The sighting is similar to another reported in Zion, Illinois, at nearly the same time,There were no detailed descriptions provided about the object,Only visual observation was recorded,Estimated speed of the object was approximately 500-700 mph,The sighting lasted around 15 minutes.
witness description: Multiple individuals reported the sighting, but no names or detailed descriptions are given.
